headline: REGENXBIO Announces Completion of Enrollment in Pivotal Trials of Subretinal Surabgene Lomparvovec for Wet AMD
summary: REGENXBIO Inc. (Nasdaq: RGNX) today announced the completion of enrollment in the ATMOSPHERE® and ASCENT® pivotal studies evaluating surabgene lomparvovec (sura-vec, ABBV-RGX-314) in wet age-related macular degeneration (wet AMD) using subretinal delivery.
